419
01:55:38,887 --> 01:55:42,069
[SPEAKER_12]: In request new increased school base from our principals and directors, we have $987,000.

420
01:55:54,660 --> 01:55:59,085
[SPEAKER_12]: For request increased facilities and operational spending, we have $554,000.

421
01:55:59,346 --> 01:56:12,221
[SPEAKER_12]: And then just based on our observation, reviewing, and certain programs that we've already paid for that we won't need to pay for next year, we have an identified savings of 400.

422
01:56:14,123 --> 01:56:19,045
[SPEAKER_12]: $90,991, which gives us a total budget proposal of $94,032,696.

423
01:56:19,666 --> 01:56:26,630
[SPEAKER_12]: And through this presentation, we'll walk you through these numbers and get to that number.

424
01:56:28,891 --> 01:56:33,234
