425
01:56:36,868 --> 01:56:39,550
[SPEAKER_12]: These cost increases, so we have two starting off the bat.

426
01:56:40,371 --> 01:56:45,636
[SPEAKER_12]: We have two teachers at the Curtis Tufts who have been hitting a short tuition revolving fund line.

427
01:56:50,039 --> 01:56:53,442
