[SPEAKER_33]: Textbooks are quite dated.

514
02:09:26,520 --> 02:09:31,521
[SPEAKER_33]: And testing and assessment materials for the World Language Program.

515
02:09:37,143 --> 02:09:38,243
[SPEAKER_33]: Another area that

516
02:09:39,856 --> 02:09:54,109
[SPEAKER_33]: is not that much money in the big scheme of things, but we feel it's very important to increase our commitment to professional development.

517
02:09:54,649 --> 02:09:59,714
