532
02:12:16,865 --> 02:12:27,173
[SPEAKER_33]: Sometimes it's training funds to bring in a subject matter expert during PD days.

533
02:12:28,635 --> 02:12:33,959
[SPEAKER_33]: It could be training and implementing certain parts of the curriculum or using

