541
02:13:54,902 --> 02:14:03,550
[SPEAKER_33]: The program's basically a very sophisticated computer program, and it's based on the number of seats that we have.

542
02:14:03,650 --> 02:14:07,313
[SPEAKER_33]: So the cost of that particular curriculum is $75,000.

543
02:14:09,550 --> 02:14:15,415
[SPEAKER_33]: And then we're also looking to implement a formal ELA curriculum in the middle school.

544
02:14:17,077 --> 02:14:35,053
