02:14:35,834 --> 02:14:39,964
[SPEAKER_33]: on what best meets the needs of Medford Public Schools.

546
02:14:43,051 --> 02:14:43,633
[SPEAKER_33]: We also

547
02:14:46,560 --> 02:14:51,343
[SPEAKER_33]: have to increase our budget for NWEA map assessments.

548
02:14:52,403 --> 02:15:07,011
