550
02:15:19,287 --> 02:15:23,552
[SPEAKER_33]: It's been very well received by our staff.

551
02:15:23,652 --> 02:15:29,097
[SPEAKER_33]: So the cost of that, we're using it for free this year and the cost going forward would be $19,500.

552
02:15:34,566 --> 02:15:41,802
