553
02:15:43,929 --> 02:15:52,195
[SPEAKER_33]: We also are way behind in implementing interactive panels throughout the school districts.

554
02:15:52,255 --> 02:16:06,747
[SPEAKER_33]: We do have them in different classrooms and we have excluded the high school in this proposal because we expect that all those classrooms will have this technology.

555
02:16:09,933 --> 02:16:21,559
[SPEAKER_33]: This cost, $180,000, would allow us to install 60 interactive panels this year.

556
02:16:21,599 --> 02:16:27,542
[SPEAKER_33]: And it's a five-year program to get the whole district outfitted with interactive panels.

557
02:16:32,765 --> 02:16:44,853
[SPEAKER_33]: We also are looking to purchase software that will improve our content protection for our students.

558
02:16:44,914 --> 02:16:56,702
