[SPEAKER_28]: Yeah.

1118
03:14:32,521 --> 03:14:33,862
[SPEAKER_38]: A couple of things have changed.

1119
03:14:34,702 --> 03:14:42,725
[SPEAKER_38]: The administrative assistant who processes these invoices in her second year and she actually now tracks the actual invoice numbers and notes what's been done.

1120
03:14:43,525 --> 03:14:50,088
[SPEAKER_38]: I'm looking to implement a tighter process as far as verifying work and verifying the invoices that it's been processed.

1121
03:14:50,868 --> 03:14:54,710
