1122
03:14:54,730 --> 03:14:55,250
[SPEAKER_38]: It's not ready.

1123
03:14:56,230 --> 03:15:06,878
[SPEAKER_38]: a greater communication with vendors to make sure that they are sending us their bills in a timely fashion, so that not only makes closing the fiscal year more appropriate, but also making sure we don't miss anything.

1124
03:15:07,739 --> 03:15:12,662
[SPEAKER_38]: So we are actively and proactively contacting vendors on a regular basis, saying, do we have all your invoices?

1125
