[SPEAKER_38]: Are you looking for anything outstanding?

1127
03:15:15,064 --> 03:15:20,868
[SPEAKER_38]: Trying to make sure that we're not missing something on our end that they may have just not sent in, or sent in incorrectly, or got in the wrong place.

1128
03:15:20,888 --> 03:15:22,950
[SPEAKER_38]: Because some of that always happens, as far as I know.

